. Web3 Digital Asset Lending L1
Overview

Web3 Digital Asset Lending L1 enables borrowing and lending of tokenized assets through decentralized infrastructure.

Features
Collateralized lending
On-chain loan agreements
Automated liquidation
Interest rate mechanisms
Asset tokenization support
Architecture
Asset Registry

Stores collateral and asset data.

Lending Engine

Manages loans and repayments.

Risk Module

Monitors collateral ratios.

Liquidation Engine

Handles default scenarios.

Use Cases
DeFi lending platforms
